{"tid":1805702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[毅進制] 6桶汽油, 51個玻璃樽, 警方估計能製造超過100枚汽油彈","createTime":"2019-12-31T18:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T06:35:10.000Z","uid":157411,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"192851bfaafb24657dc97bd552717227b3e1c8b0","tid":1805702,"uid":157411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"警方今日（31 日）在慈雲山沙田坳對出的一個山坡上，搜獲 6 桶懷疑汽油、51 個空玻璃瓶，警方估計相關原材料能製造超過 100 枚汽油彈，或在今晚或明日的公眾活動中使用，以引起恐慌及混亂。東九龍重案組總督察王爾威稱，警察總部刑事部今日拘捕數人，及後從被捕人口中得知事件，警方正調查儲存危險品時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%AA%A2%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E6%9E%9A%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E5%8E%9F%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99-%E6%8C%87%E6%88%96%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%8E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A3%BD%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C/?fbclid=IwAR0Ien8dhDzJS32CczSusjJRR4l_S5fpTF6LmLqfllVZCiQIjbrUSi8YB7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%259E%259A%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%258E%259F%25E6%259D%2590%25E6%2596%2599-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2585%258C%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Ien8dhDzJS32CczSusjJRR4l_S5fpTF6LmLqfllVZCiQIjbrUSi8YB7s&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=5fa0b65c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E6%259E%259A%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%258E%259F%25E6%259D%2590%25E6%2596%2599-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2585%258C%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Ien8dhDzJS32CczSusjJRR4l_S5fpTF6LmLqfllVZCiQIjbrUSi8YB7s&h=1d6686e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%AA%A2%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E6%9E%9A%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88